---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About" 
  description="We believe the future isn't something that happens to us—it's something we create together."
>
  <section class="container py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-12 gradient-meridian bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        The Work That Matters
      </h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-headings:text-meridian-burgundy max-w-none">
        <p class="text-2xl font-light leading-relaxed text-meridian-steel mb-8">
          The world doesn't need another think tank. It needs architects of possibility—
          people brave enough to imagine what could be and skilled enough to build it.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-meridian-light-gray p-8 rounded-lg my-12">
          <p class="text-xl font-medium text-meridian-dark mb-0">
            "Progress happens at the intersection of the inevitable and the impossible. 
            Our job is to expand what we believe is possible."
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">We Are Project Meridian</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
          We exist at the confluence of strategy and transformation. Not consultants who 
          diagnose from a distance, but partners who roll up our sleeves and build alongside you.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          Our work spans the spectrum of human ambition: from reimagining organizations 
          to redesigning systems, from challenging assumptions to creating new realities.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Our Operating System</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-meridian-burgundy pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Start With Humans</h3>
            <p>Technology is just a tool. Organizations are just structures. 
            Real change happens when people decide to show up differently.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-l-4 border-meridian-burgundy pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Question Everything</h3>
            <p>The most dangerous phrase in any language is "we've always done it this way." 
            Progress demands that we challenge what is to create what could be.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-l-4 border-meridian-burgundy pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Build in Public</h3>
            <p>Transformation isn't a spectator sport. We share our work, our thinking, 
            and yes, our failures—because collective intelligence beats individual brilliance every time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">The Invitation</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
          This isn't just our blog. It's a laboratory for ideas that refuse to behave. 
          A gathering place for rebels with a cause. A workshop where the future takes shape.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          Whether you're here to challenge your thinking, find kindred spirits, or discover 
          what's next—welcome. The best conversations happen when diverse minds collide.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-meridian-burgundy text-white p-8 rounded-lg my-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Join the Expedition</h3>
          <p class="text-lg mb-4">
            Great work rarely happens in isolation. If you're building something that matters, 
            we want to hear about it.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn bg-white text-meridian-burgundy hover:bg-meridian-light-gray">
              Start a Conversation
            </a>
            <a href="/rss.xml" class="btn border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-meridian-burgundy">
              Subscribe to Updates
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <p class="text-xl font-light text-meridian-steel">
            Ready to stop predicting the future and start inventing it?
          </p>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold mt-4 text-meridian-burgundy">
            Let's begin.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>